cent%20win.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Read%20the%20pitch%20deck%20Instacart%20veterans%20used%20to%20raise%20%248.5%20million%20for%20AI%20startup%20Champ%20AI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226869%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Champ%20AI%20cofounders%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a024a64ba7ef34b41f37315%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChamp%20AI%20cofounders%20Peter%20Lin%2C%20Jagannath%20Putrevu%2C%20and%20Ted%20Cheng.%3Cp%3EChamp%20AI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChamp%20AI%20has%20emerged%20from%20stealth%20with%20%248.5%20million%20in%20funding%20led%20by%20Redpoint%20Ventures.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIts%20three%20cofounders%20spent%20nearly%20a%20decade%20as%20engineers%20at%20Instacart.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChamp%20AI%20uses%20AI%20agents%20to%20automate%20phone%20calls%2C%20paperwork%2C%20and%20browser%20tasks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20nearly%20a%20decade%20as%20engineers%20at%20Instacart%2C%20Champ%20AI's%20founders%20learned%20a%20painful%20lesson%3A%20scaling%20a%20company%20can%20mean%20drowning%20in%20back-office%20busywork.%20Now%20they've%20raised%20%248.5%20million%20to%20build%20AI%20agents%20that%20automate%20the%20work%20of%20back-office%20operations%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20seen%20firsthand%20how%20operations%20teams%20deal%20with%20lots%20of%20manual%20processes%20and%20really%20struggle%20as%20a%20company%20scales%2C%26quot%3B%20Champ%20AI%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20Jagannath%20Putrevu%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20There%20were%20orders%20to%20fix%2C%20store%20hours%20to%20update%2C%20fraud%20issues%20to%20investigate%2C%20and%20customer-support%20policies%20to%20follow.%20Much%20of%20that%20work%20required%20operations%20employees%20to%20tediously%20move%20between%20documents%2C%20internal%20systems%2C%20forms%2C%20and%20phone%20calls%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPutrevu%20and%20his%20cofounders%2C%20Ted%20Cheng%20and%20Peter%20Lin%2C%20founded%20Champ%20AI%20last%20year%20to%20automate%20that%20work%20for%20other%20companies.%20The%20startup%20has%20come%20out%20of%20stealth%20with%20%248.5%20million%20in%20funding%20led%20by%20Redpoint%20Ventures%2C%20with%20participation%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fdefy.vc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edefy.vc%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20SV%20Angel.%20They%20also%20secured%20an%20angel%20investment%20from%20their%20former%20boss%2C%20Instacart%20cofounder%20Max%20Mullen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChamp's%20software%20can%20turn%20a%20company's%20internal%20policies%20into%20actions%20a%20computer%20can%20perform%2C%20such%20as%20logging%20into%20websites%2C%20clicking%20buttons%2C%20downloading%20documents%2C%20filling%20out%20spreadsheets%2C%20sending%20emails%2C%20and%20making%20phone%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20agent%20is%20both%20the%20brain%20and%20the%20hands%2C%20so%20it%20decides%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20and%20then%20gets%20it%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20Putrevu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChamp%20AI%20has%20more%20than%2010%20paying%20customers%20across%20logistics%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20e-commerce%2C%20Putrevu%20said.%20Arena%20Club%2C%20a%20sports%20and%20entertainment%20card%20marketplace%2C%20said%20using%20Champ%20AI%20has%20sped%20up%20its%20card-processing%20work%20by%2030%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChamp%20AI%20is%20entering%20a%20crowded%20market.%20It%20will%20compete%20with%20incumbents%20such%20as%20UiPath%2C%20Automation%20Anywhere%2C%20and%20Microsoft%20Power%20Automate%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20new%20crop%20of%20AI-agent%20startups%20tackling%20browser%20work%20and%20customer%20support.%20Champ%20is%20also%20going%20after%20work%20traditionally%20handled%20by%20business%20outsourcing%20firms%2C%20many%20of%20which%20rely%20on%20large%20overseas%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPutrevu%20said%20Champ%20is%20not%20designed%20to%20replace%20operations%20teams.%20Companies%20still%20need%20people%20to%20own%20processes%2C%20monitor%20agents%2C%20and%20manage%20their%20performance.%20But%20he%20said%20the%20software%20can%20help%20them%20avoid%20spending%20months%20getting%20outsourced%20teams%20up%20to%20speed%20and%20instead%20keep%20more%20operations%20in-house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20already%20have%20customers%20who%2C%20whenever%20they're%20thinking%20of%20launching%20a%20new%20product%2C%20come%20to%20us%20first%20and%20set%20it%20up%20on%20Champ%2C%26quot%3B%20Putrevu%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20software%20helps%20customers%20launch%20products%20in%20weeks%20instead%20of%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChamp%20has%20six%20employees%20and%20plans%20to%20use%20the%20funding%20to%20hire%20software%20engineers%2C%20forward-deployed%20engineers%2C%20and%20salespeople.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECheck%20out%20the%20pitch%20deck%20that%20Champ%20AI%20used%20to%20raise%20its%20%248.5%20million%20seed%20round%3A%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222394%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Champ%20AI%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a024ddae1443b8dc48e40ed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221340%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EChamp%20AI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222392%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Champ%20AI%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a024e20e1443b8dc48e40f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221342%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EChamp%20AI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222392%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Champ%20AI%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a024e20e1443b8dc48e40f3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221340%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECham