22A%20commencement%20speaker%20who%20praised%20AI%20was%20booed%20at%20humanities%20graduation%3A%20'I%20struck%20a%20chord'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222892%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gloria%20Caulfield%20speaks%20onstage%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Central%20Florida's%20Spring%202026%20Commencement.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0317d7c9dd4cb81cda9793%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221630%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGloria%20Caulfield%2C%20pictured%20here%2C%20turned%20away%20from%20the%20crowd%20and%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20happened%3F%26quot%3B%20upon%20hearing%20the%20boos.%3Cp%3EScreenshot%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Central%20Florida's%20YouTube%20livestream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGloria%20Caulfield's%20speech%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Central%20Florida's%20spring%20commencement%20hit%20a%20nerve.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20Caulfield%20said%20AI%20is%20the%20next%20industrial%20revolution%2C%20a%20crowd%20of%20graduates%20booed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20reaction%20to%20the%20speech%20revealed%20a%20growing%20divide%20between%20tech%20optimism%20and%20AI%20anxiety.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20optimists%20have%20been%20reminded%20that%20not%20everyone%20sees%20the%20technology%20as%20a%20force%20for%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20speaker%20was%20booed%20onstage%20after%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BAI%20is%20the%20next%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblackstone-jon-gray-impact-artificial-intelligence-jobs-business-presentation-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eindustrial%20revolution%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Central%20Florida's%20spring%20commencement%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20happened%3F%20OK%2C%20I%20struck%20a%20chord%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gloria%20Caulfield%2C%20the%20speaker%20and%20Vice%20President%20of%20real%20estate%20firm%20Strategic%20Alliances%20for%20Tavistock%20Development%20company%2C%20upon%20hearing%20the%20boos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20AI%20was%20not%20a%20factor%20in%20our%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20Caulfield%20continued.%20This%20time%2C%20she%20was%20met%20with%20cheers%20from%20the%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reaction%20to%20the%20speech%20highlights%20a%20growing%20disconnect%20between%20proponents%20of%20AI%20and%20those%20who%20feel%20they%20have%20gotten%20the%20short%20end%20of%20the%20AI%20stick.%20Since%20the%20start%20of%20this%20year%2C%20at%20least%2012%20major%20companies%20that%20have%20cut%20their%20workforces%20have%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flist-companies-replacing-human-employees-with-ai-layoffs-workforce-reductions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecited%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0as%20a%20reason%20for%20layoffs.%20One%20recent%20poll%20indicated%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-people-ai-threat-jobs-harvard-youth-poll-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esome%20young%20Americans%3C%2Fa%3E%20see%20the%20technology%20as%C2%A0a%20threat%C2%A0to%20their%20job%20prospects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECaulfield%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Central%20Florida%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Ethe%20tech%20world%20has%20genuinely%20not%20grappled%20with%20how%20many%20people%3Cbr%3Edespise%20them%20and%20what%20they%20make%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Ft2VIuYEjLW%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Ft2VIuYEjLW%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20onion%20person%20(%40CantEverDie)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCantEverDie%2Fstatus%2F205370515691553