the%20terrifying%20so-called%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaring-aging-elderly-parents-millennials-nursing-home-cost-women-daughters-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emillennial%20daughter%20tax%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20some%2C%20the%20solution%20to%20elder%20care%20is%20looking%20abroad.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeter%20and%20Rita%20Millard%20have%20spent%20the%20past%20few%20years%20in%20a%20care%20facility%20in%20northern%20Thailand%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretirees-left-america-moved-to-chiang-mai-slower-affordable-life-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20hotspot%20for%20retirees%20from%20around%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Peter%20told%20BI%20that%20living%20in%20the%20facility%2C%20where%20a%20resident's%20average%20monthly%20cost%20is%20about%20%241%2C914%2C%20is%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretiree-couple-moved-to-senior-care-resort-thailand-chiang-mai-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Binsurance%20policy%26quot%3B%20for%20whoever%20gets%20left%20behind%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMexico%20has%20also%20proven%20to%20be%20a%20more%20affordable%20option%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-seniors-to-mexico-long-term-care-costs-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong-term%20elder%20care%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Costs%20for%20assisted%20living%20in%20the%20country%20averages%20between%20%241%2C000%20to%20%242%2C000%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20have%20found%20strength%20in%20numbers%2C%20bringing%20multiple%20generations%20under%20one%20roof%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fthe-new-american-home%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20trend%20BI%20has%20covered%20extensively%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Multigenerational%20households%20can%20ease%20the%20financial%20pressures%20of%20childcare%20