ssinsider.com%2Finside-spotify-wrapped-team-creation-process-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebeloved%20Wrapped%20rollout%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Spotify%20users%20can%20now%20see%20their%20all-time%20top%20songs%2C%20along%20with%20a%20handful%20of%20other%20nostalgic%20surprises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20an%20opportunity%20for%20us%20to%20give%20back%20and%20make%20people%20connect%20with%20their%20time%20on%20Spotify%2C%26quot%3B%20Marc%20Hazan%2C%20SVP%20of%20marketing%20and%20partnerships%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20help%20soundtrack%20people's%20lives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221180%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Spotify's%20%26quot%3BParty%20of%20the%20Year(s)%26quot%3B%20is%20pictured%2C%20showing%20the%20number%20of%20songs%20a%20user%20streamed.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a021fdeba7ef34b41f37144%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221510%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESpotify's%20%26quot%3BParty%20of%20the%20Year(s)%26quot%3B%20shows%20users%20how%20many%20songs%20they've%20streamed.%3Cp%3ESpotify%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2268bc51d1-6726-4cca-8b22-ab4ccdc8951e%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20find%20your%20own%20%26quot%3BParty%20of%20the%20Year(s)%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20its%20annual%20Wrapped%20feature%2C%20Spotify%20is%20taking%20its%20users%20back%20to%20day%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BSpotify%2020%3A%20Your%20Party%20of%20the%20Year(s)%26quot%3B%20package%20includes%20the%20user's%20first%20day%20on%20Spotify%20and%20the%20first%20song%20they%20streamed.%20For%20those%20looking%20for%20pure%20numbers%2C%20Spotify%20also%20includes%20the%20total%20number%20of%20songs%20a%20user%20has%20listened%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspotify-wrapped-2025-metrics-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclassics%20of%20Wrapped%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20the%20user's%20most-streamed%20artist.%20Users%20will%20also%20have%20access%20to%20an%20All-Time%20Top%20Songs%20Playlist%2C%20featuring%20the%20top%20120%20songs%20and%20their%20play%20counts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Wrapped%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BParty%20of%20the%20Year(s)%26quot%3B%20is%20built%20to%20be%20posted%20on%20other%20platforms.%20The%20package%20includes%20custom%20social%20media%20share%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221179%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Spotify%20%26quot%3BParty%20of%20the%20Year(s)%26quot%3B%20is%20pictured%2C%20feature%20the%20first%20day%20a%20user%20was%20on%20Spotify.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a02201bc9dd4cb81cda93e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221698%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20%26quot%3BParty%20of%20the%20Year(s)%26quot%3B%20dates%20back%20to%20the%20user's%20first%20day%20on%20Spotify.%3Cp%3ESpotify%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20access%20the%20data%20package%2C%20users%20can%20search%20%26quot%3BSpotify%2020%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BParty%20of%20the%20Year(s)%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20Spotify%20mobile%20app.%20They%20can%20also%20visit%20spotify.com%2F20%20on%20a%20mobile%20browser.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d813d801-977d-4133-b3dd-27111b867e0c%5C%22%3EWhy%20Spotify%20chose%20to%20celebrate%20with%20data%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETwenty%20years%20is%20a%20blockbuster%20anniversary.%20Spotify's%20celebration%20is%20relatively%20quiet%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20that%20was%20intentional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHazan%20said%20that%20the%20team%20%26quot%3Bdidn't%20want%20to%20make%20it%20about%20us.%26quot%3B%20The%20goal%20was%20to%20honor%20the%20user's%20experience%2C%20not%20to%20%26quot%3Bpop%20the%20champagne%20and%20pat%20each%20other%20on%20the%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20they%20wanted%20the%20campaign%20to%20be%20celebratory.%20Hazan%20said%20the%20teams%20involved%20%E2%80%94%20including%20product%2C%20communications%2C%20marketing%2C%20music%2C%20and%20more%20%E2%80%94%20went%20for%20maximum%20color.%20They%20also%20chose%20to%20make%20the%20disco%20ball%20a%20primary%20image%20of%20the%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20about%20six%20months%20to%20bring%20the%20campaign%20together%2C%20Hazan%20said.%20Many%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-see-spotify-wrapped-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWrapped%20planners%3C%2Fa%3E%20contributed%2C%20along%20with%20other%20Spotify%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22863%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Spotify's%20%26quot%3BParty%20of%20the%20Year(s)%26quot%3B%20campaign%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a022703ba7ef34b41f37178%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221314%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Spotify%20campaign%20includes%20graphics%20designed%20for%20social%20media%2C%20like%20Wrapped.%3Cp%3ESpotify%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%20are%20Spotify%20users%20so%20obsessed%20with%20data%3F%20Wrapped%20is%20one%20of%20their%20biggest%20campaigns%2C%20after%20all%2C%20and%20Hazan%20said%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bjust%20gets%20bigger%20and%20bigger%20and%20bigger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHazan%20compared%20music%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fviral-stadium-moments-astronomer-ceo-us-open-phillies-karen-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20sports%20team%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Fans%20want%20baseball%20caps%20and%20jerseys%20to%20show%20their%20allegiance%3B%20in%20the%20same%20way%2C%20music%20fans%20want%20to%20post%20their%20top%20songs%20and%20artists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20badge%2C%26quot%3B%20Hazan%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20a%20Lady%20Gaga%20fan%20or%20a%20Swiftie%2C%20you%20want%20to%20show%20the%20world%20or%20show%20your%20friends%20that%20that's%20who%20you%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%2020th%20anniversary%20passes%2C%20there's%20no%20big%20plan%20for%20the%2025th%20yet.