20is%20lit%20up%20orange%20as%20a%20figure%20fires%20a%20gun%20in%20the%20air%20in%20a%20field%20at%20night%20time%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a01b1c0ba7ef34b41f36ebe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223996%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkrainian%20soldiers%20see%20numerous%20drones%20on%20the%20battlefield%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20always%20clear%20which%20side%20they%20belong%20to.%3Cp%3ERoman%20PILIPEY%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUkrainian%20soldiers%20say%20they%20sometimes%20destroy%20any%20drone%20they%20see%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20their%20own.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUkrainian%20drones%20are%20mistaken%20for%20Russian%2C%20resulting%20in%20friendly%20fire%20incidents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDrone%20makers%20say%20it's%20an%20expected%20part%20of%20such%20a%20chaotic%20fight.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20soldiers%20sometimes%20wind%20up%20taking%20out%20their%20own%20side's%20drones%20on%20the%20war's%20chaotic%20battlefields%2C%20where%20it%20isn't%20always%20clear%20if%20the%20weapons%20buzzing%20above%20them%20are%20friend%20or%20foe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoldiers%20say%20that%20in%20moments%20of%20uncertainty%2C%20they%20may%20have%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20open%20fire%20on%20any%20drone%20they%20see%2C%20disable%20all%20radio-frequency%20drones%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhidden-electronic-warfare-battle-demanding-more-of-ukrainian-soldiers-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eelectronic%20warfare%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20sever%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-adds-fiber-optic-wires-molniya-drones-makes-them-unjammable-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econtrol%20cables%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20unjammable%20fiber-optic%20drones%20without%20knowing%20the%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFriendly%20fire%20and%20friendly%20electronic%20warfare%20influence%20are%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20causes%20of%20loss%20of%20equipment%20on%20the%20front%20line.%20It's%20true%2C%26quot%3B%20Mykyta%20Rozhkov%2C%20the%20chief%20business%20development%20officer%20of%20Frontline%20Robotics%2C%20a%20Ukrainian%20drone%20and%20weapons%20maker%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20losses%20are%20understandable%2C%20though%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20end%2C%20if%20something%20looks%20like%20a%20drone%20and%20is%20coming%20your%20way%20and%20it's%20less%20than%20100%20meters%20from%20you%2C%20maybe%20it's%20better%20to%20shoot%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20other%20losses%2C%20it's%20just%20a%20part%20of%20how%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-knocks-down-russian-drones-uk-taking-notes-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eintense%20and%20drone-heavy%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20playing%20out%2C%20companies%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStanislav%20Hryshyn%2C%20the%20cofounder%20of%20Ukrainian%20drone%20maker%20General%20Cherry%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20people%20%26quot%3Bneed%20to%20understand%20that%20the%20battleground%20is%20total%20hell%2C%20the%20toughest%20place%20in%20the%20world%2C%20the%20scariest%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225564%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20figures%20in%20camouflage%20gear%20stand%20in%20a%20field%20with%20bare%20trees%20and%20a%20blue%20sky%20behind%20them%20with%20a%20drone%20hovering%20above%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a02e0aaba7ef34b41f37435%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223709%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDrones%20are%20a%20key%20weapon%20for%20both%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine.%3Cp%3ESerhii%20Mykhalchuk%2FGlobal%20Images%20Ukraine%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20how%20many%20Ukrainian%20drones%20are%20lost%20to%20friendly%20fire%3B%20however%2C%20soldiers%20have%20said%20that%20there%20are%20often%20so%20many%20drones%20in%20the%20sky%20that%20it%20causes%20panic%20and%20confusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-can-jam-own-drones-many-some-russian-share-signals-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etaking%20down%20a%20friendly%20drone%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20accident%2C%20especially%20considering%20the%20intensity%20of%20the%20electronic%20warfare%20fight%3B%20other%20times%2C%20it's%20intentional.%20In%20the%20heat%20of%20battle%2C%20soldiers%20may%20panic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-soldiers-can-panic-jam-everything-confused-about-drones-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejam%20everything%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20soldiers%20told%20BI%20previously%20that%20troops%20will%20also%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-west-needs-more-cheap-weapons-counter-russia-and-china-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20cut%20the%20cables%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20fiber-optic%20drones%20built%20to%20survive%20electronic%20warfare%20with%20a%20better-safe-than-sorry%20attitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20use%20scissors%2C%20knives%2C%20or%20their%20bare%20hands%2C%20with%20one%20soldier%20saying%20that%20every%20member%20of%20his%20unit%20carries%20scissors%20for%20this%20purpose%20and%20that%20he%20bought%20them%20all%20retractors%20so%20no%20one%20would%20lose%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFacing%20these%20challenges%2C%20drone%20operators%20will%20sometimes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraines-electronic-warfare-fight-drone-pilots-must-sort-safe-paths-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emessage%20nearby%20units%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20negotiate%20times%20and%20directions%20for%20safe%20passage%20to%20stop%20their%20drones%20from%20being%20downed%20by%20friendly%20defenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20small%20black%20drone%20in%20a%20blue%20and%20cloudy%20sky%20with%20a%20thin%20white%20wire%20coming%20down%20from%20inside%20it%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a02e121e1443b8dc48e41fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFiber-optic%20drones%20are%20controlled%20by%20a%20cable%20that%20soldiers%20can%20cut.%3Cp%3EViktor%20Fridshon%2FGlobal%20Images%20Ukraine%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20is%20less%20apparent%20with%20Ukraine's%20ground%20drones%2C%20also%20known%20as%20ground%20robots%20or%20unmanned%20ground%20vehicles%20(UGVs)%2C%20which%20are%20a%20small%20but%20rapidly%20growing%20part%20of%20Ukraine's%20arsenal.%20DevDroid%2C%20one%20maker%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20while%20it%20doesn't%20believe%20that%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20are%20deliberately%20targeting%20its%20drones%20out%20of%20confusion%2C%20there%20were%20still%20some%20friendly%20fire%20mistakes.%20Oleg%20Fedoryshyn%2C%20the%20company's%20director%20of%20R%26amp%3BD%2C%20called%20them%20%26quot%3Bsmall%20friendly%20accidents.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20been%20working%20to%20improve%20battlefield%20coordination%20through%20its%20Delta%20system%2C%20an%20online%20battlefield%20management%20system%20which%20provides%20an%20overall%20picture%20of%20the%20fight%2C%20including%20where%20Russian%20targets%20are%20and%20how%20to%20coordinate%20Ukraine's%20forces.%20It%20includes%20a%20layer%20dedicated%20to%20the%20awareness%20and%20management%20of%20Ukraine's%20drones%20that%20could%20reduce%20friendly%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227854%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20stands%20beside%20a%20large%20weapon%20against%20a%20night%20sky%20lit%20up%20by%20red%20light%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a02e028c9dd4cb81cda96b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225239%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20are%20so%20many%20drones%20in%20the%20sky%20that%20soldiers%20can%20struggle%20to%20tell%20which%20side%20they%20belong%20to.%3Cp%3EMaksym%20Kishka%2FFrontliner%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDrones%20are%20also%20built%20to%20be%20expendable%2C%20though%2C%20and%20losses%20are%20expected.%20Drones%20are%20far%20cheaper%20than%20the%20high-end%20gear%20that%20Western%20militaries%20have%20traditionally%20relied%20on%2C%20and%20that's%20a%20deliberate%20feature%20of%20how%20they%20are%20built%20and%20how%20they%20are%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERozhkov%20said%20powerful%20missiles%20still%20have%20a%20place%20on%20the%20battlefield%2C%20but%20Ukraine's%20experience%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Iran%20war%2C%20shows%20that%20countries%20also%20need%20weapons%20that%20can%20be%20produced%20quickly%20and%20used%20at%20scale%2C%20like%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20kind%20of%20mass%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20manage%20and%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFriendly-fire%20losses%20can%20create%20more%20demand%20for%20drone%20makers%20because%20destroyed%20drones%20have%20to%20be%20replaced.%20The%20companies%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20said%20that%20the%20upside%20is%20limited.%20Ukraine's%20defense%20budget%20is%20stretched%2C%20Russian%20jamming%20and%20interception%20already%20consume%20huge%20numbers%20of%20drones%2C%20and%20some%20companies%20said%20they%20provide%20drones%20to%20units%20for%20free.%20But%20losing%20those%20systems%20to%20friendly%20fire%20or%20some%20other%20impact%20on%20the%20mission%20is%20just%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20drone%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-soldiers-friendly-fire-drone-losses-weapons-makers-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778585849000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a01b1f6ba7ef34b41f36ebf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-soldiers-friendly-fire-drone-losses-weapons-makers-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20chaotic%20fight%20with%20Russia%20means%20Ukraine's%20tr