ay%20post.%20The%20'Baby%20Driver'%20star%2C%20who%20welcomed%20his%20first%20child%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20shared%20intimate%20glimpses%20of%20their%20family%20life.%20Elgort%2C%20known%20for%20his%20privacy%2C%20confirmed%20his%20fatherhood%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20describing%20the%20experience%20as%20exhilarating%20and%20life-changing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20mom%20and%20I%20do%20the%20Wordle%20puzzle%20every%20day.%20It's%20an%20easy%20way%20for%20us%20to%20stay%20connected.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20poses%20with%20her%20mother.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a030929c9dd4cb81cda974e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENo%20matter%20what's%20happening%20in%20their%20lives%2C%20the%20author%20says%20she%20and%20her%20mother%20connect%20by%20playing%20Wordle%20every%20day.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Andrea%20Javor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20mom%20and%20I%20have%20played%20the%20Wordle%20puzzle%20game%20every%20day%20for%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20has%20been%20an%20easy%2C%20low-stakes%20way%20for%20us%20to%20stay%20connected%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20is%20going%20on.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESure%2C%20we'll%20be%20watching%20the%20new%20primetime%20show%2C%20but%20I%20know%20we'll%20continue%20our%20daily%20ritual%2C%20too.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENBC%20just%20announced%20that%20they%20are%20launching%20a%20new%20game%20show%20based%20on%20Wordle%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-wordle-puzzle-game-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epopular%20word%20puzzle%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwordle-trackers-ads-new-york-times-ownership-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ELong%20before%20it%20was%20heading%20for%20primetime%2C%20I%20delighted%20in%20the%20daily%205-letter%20puzzle%20while%20strategizing%20the%20best%20starting%20word%20%E2%80%94%20ocean%2C%20adieu%2C%20house%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94%20and%20hoping%20I'd%20solve%20it%20efficiently%20and%20keep%20my%20daily%20streak%20going.%20Each%20guess%20is%20an%20act%20of%20faith%2C%20believing%20the%20right%20word%20is%20waiting%20to%20be%20solved%20successfully.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EBut%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fheirlooms-photos-helped-uncover-family-past-connect-with-mom-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereal%20ritual%3C%2Fa%3E%20that's%20mattered%20most%20to%20me%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20guessing%20five%20letters%3B%20it's%20the%20daily%20Wordle%20text%20thread%20I've%20kept%20with%20my%20mom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2211ab27f5-c519-47f5-82f4-30805adc53bc%5C%22%3EMy%20family%20has%20always%20had%20a%20love%20of%20games%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGames%20have%20always%20been%20a%20part%20of%20my%20family's%20routine.%20Growing%20up%2C%20I%20was%20the%20oldest%20of%2013%20cousins%20on%20my%20mom's%20side%20and%20remember%20running%20around%20my%20grandparents'%20house%20while%20my%20parents%2C%20grandparents%2C%20aunts%2C%20and%20uncles%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplay-board-video-games-more-older-kids-than-toddlers-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplayed%20games%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Spades%2C%20Euchre%2C%20and%20Trivial%20Pursuit.%20Being%20old%20enough%20to%20learn%20the%20card%20game%20Oh%20Hell%20felt%20like%20a%20rite%20of%20passage%20in%20my%20tween%20years%20and%20readied%20me%20to%20sit%20across%20from%20the%20adults%20at%20the%20grown-ups'%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20adult%2C%20the%20gaming%20tradition%20has%20continued.%20I%20don't%20remember%20who%20found%20Wordle%20first%2C%20but%20my%20mom%20and%20I%20have%20both%20been%20hooked%20since%20it%20was%20in%20its%20early%20beta%20phase.%20Every%20morning%20for%20the%20past%20several%20years%2C%20without%20ever%20skipping%20a%20day%2C%20my%20mom%20has%20sent%20me%20her%20results%20of%20the%20game.%20If%20she%20doesn't%20solve%20the%20puzzle%2C%20I%20typically%20get%20a%20surprise-face%20emoji%20or%20a%20funny%20caveat%20like%20%26quot%3BI%20hate%20double%20consonants%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Btoo%20many%20possibilities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20and%20her%20mother.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0309a8c9dd4cb81cda9752%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20said%20her%20family%20has%20always%20loved%20playing%20games%20and%20said%20she%20was%20excited%20when%20she%20was%20old%20enough%20to%20join%20the%20adult%20table.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Andrea%20Javor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223f27103c-dbc3-4131-8634-c62c93845ff3%5C%22%3EThe%20game%20has%20been%20an%20easy%20way%20to%20stay%20connected%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mom%20and%20I%20live%20in%20the%20same%20city%20and%20see%20each%20other%20a%20few%20times%20a%20month%2C%20but%20our%20lives%20don't%20overlap%20the%20way%20they%20once%20did.%20I%20don't%20have%20kids%20like%20my%20two%20brothers%20do%2C%20which%20means%20she's%20regularly%20pulled%20into%20their%20orbit%20of%20practices%2C%20games%2C%20and%20school%20events.%20Without%20anything%20similar%20to%20offer%20her%2C%20Wordle%20has%20become%20a%20low%E2%80%91effort%2C%20no%E2%80%91pressure%20reason%20to%20reach%20out%20every%20single%20day%2C%20even%20when%20there's%20nothing%20urgent%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20when%20I'm%20driving%20to%20work%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20I'll%20see%20a%20text%20message%20pop%20up%20from%20her%20on%20the%20dashboard%2C%20and%20I'll%20use%20voice-activation%20to%20listen%20to%20the%20message.%20I'll%20chuckle%20to%20myself%20when%20the%20monotone%20audio%20starts%20by%20saying%20%26quot%3BWordle%201%2C787%204%2F6%20%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20what%20I%20appreciate%20most%20about%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-son-built-successful-business-together-fought-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erelationship%20with%20my%20mom%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20I%20can%20connect%20with%20her%20anytime%2C%20about%20anything%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20mundane%20the%20topic%2C%20and%20she's%20always%20happy%20to%20interact%20with%20me.%20Our%20relationship%20reminds%20me%20of%20how%20close%20I%20was%20to%20my%20grandma%20(my%20mom's%20mom)%20when%20she%20was%20alive.%20I%20could%20sit%20at%20her%20table%2C%20shuffling%20a%20deck%20of%20cards%2C%20and%20she'd%20join%20me%20for%20a%20game%20of%20Gin%20Rummy%20%E2%80%94%20no%20formal%20invitation%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222316%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20and%20her%20mother.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a030a1ec9dd4cb81cda9754%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221737%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20said%20she%20looks%20forward%20to%20hearing%20how%20her%20mom%20does%20on%20the%20Wordle%20puzzle%20each%20day.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Andrea%20Javor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c70c67ab-bdfd-4f78-ba8b-9307ec140bf0%5C%22%3EWe're%20excited%20to%20see%20the%20show%2C%20but%20sticking%20to%20our%20format%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Wordle%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.today.com%2Fvideo%2Fjimmy-fallon-unveils-wordle-game-show-with-savannah-guthrie-263091269798%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheads%20to%20primetime%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20complete%20with%20buzzers%20and%20prize%20money%2C%20I%20can't%20help%20but%20think%20about%20what%20made%20the%20game%20special%20long%20before%20producers%20got%20involved.%20It%20was%20the%20way%20a%20simple%20puzzle%20appeared%2