ing%20a%20spike%20in%20interest%20for%20hybrids.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20to%20buy%20a%20cheap%20car%3F%20Good%20luck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAffordable%20vehicles%20%E2%80%94%20new%20or%20used%20%E2%80%94%20are%20becoming%20harder%20to%20find%20in%20American%20dealership%20lots%2C%20according%20to%20fresh%20data%20from%20online%20automotive%20marketplace%20CarGurus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20the%20average%20listing%20price%20for%20a%20new%20vehicle%20climbed%20to%20%2450%2C400%2C%20up%201%25%20from%20a%20year%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fused-car-prices-tariffs-supply-chain-automakers-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUsed-car%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20often%20viewed%20as%20a%20key%20gauge%20of%20vehicle%20affordability%2C%20are%20also%20under%20pressure%2C%20rising%20to%20nearly%20%2430%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20the%20highest%20level%20since%20August%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrices%20have%20taken%20the%20spotlight%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Kevin%20Roberts%2C%20the%20firm's%20director%20of%20economic%20and%20market%20intelligence%2C%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20affordability%20pressures%20continue%20to%20shape%20the%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAffordable%20vehicles%20haven't%20disappeared%20entirely.%20Models%20like%20the%20Nissan%20Sentra%2C%20Hyundai%20Elantra%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoyota-corolla-car-review-sleek-modern-still-affordable-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EToyota%20Corolla%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Honda%20Civic%20still%20start%20below%20or%20near%20%2430%2C000%2C%20while%20used-car%20buyers%20can%20still%20find%20lower-priced%20inventory%20in%20older%2C%20higher-mileage%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20analysts%20say%20those%20options%20are%20becoming%20less%20common.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20lower-cost%20vehicles%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20Mitsubishi%20Mirage%2C%20Nissan%20Versa%2C%20and%20Kia%20Soul%20%E2%80%94%20have%20either%20been%20discontinued%20or%20are%20being%20phased%20out%20of%20the%20US%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Americans%20continue%20gravitating%20toward%20larger%2C%20more%20expensive%20trucks%20and%20SUVs%2C%20which%20tend%20to%20generate%20higher%20profit%20margins%20for%20automakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20recent%20analysis%20from%20Moody's%2C%20the%20US%20auto%20market%20has%20become%20increasingly%20dependent%20on%20wealthier%20households%20buying%20pricier%20vehicles.%20The%20ratings%20firm%20said%20rising%20vehicle%20prices%20and%20consumers'%20preference%20for%20trucks%20and%20SUVs%20have%20reshaped%20the%20market%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReliance%20on%20financially%20stronger%20buyers%20stabilizes%20revenue%20and%20supports%20profitability%20for%20US%20automakers%2C%20but%20ties%20performance%20closely%20to%20a%20narrow%20customer%20segment%2C%26quot%3B%20Moody's%20said%20in%20a%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarGurus%20said%20that%20shift%20is%20also%20reflected%20in%20which%20cars%20are%20appearing%20at%20American%20dealerships.%20The%20share%20of%20sub-%2460%2C000%20inventory%20shrank%20by%202%25%20in%20April%2C%20helping%20push%20average%20vehicle%20prices%20even%20higher.%20Meanwhile%2C%20inventory%20for%20new%20vehicles%20priced%20above%20%2470%2C000%20has%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222e42c1a9-014f-44a9-868a-57d9cabcf5e8%5C%22%3EGas%20prices%20are%20figuring%20in%2C%20too%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228057%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20SUV%20pulls%20out%20of%20a%20gas%20station%20parking%20lot.%20The%20station's%20sign%20shows%20prices%20from%20%246.59%20to%20%246.98%20a%20gallon.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a024a6de1443b8dc48e40d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGas%20prices%20have%20been%20rapidly%20increasing%20since%20March.%20That's%20renewed%20some%20interest%20in%20fuel-efficient%20vehicles.%3Cp%3EMario%20Tama%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2028%2C%20the%20national%20average%20price%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmap-compares-gas-price-state-us-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egallon%20of%20regular%20gasoline%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20%242.98%2C%20according%20to%20AAA.%20By%20Monday%2C%20that%20figure%20had%20climbed%20to%20%244.52.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20fuel%20costs%20rise%2C%20shoppers%20are%20increasingly%20turning%20toward%20hybrids%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigher-gas-prices-lift-interest-in-electric-cars-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eand%20electric%20vehicles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20CarGurus%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20views%20of%20new%20EVs%20and%20hybrids%20accounted%20for%2020%25%20of%20shopper%20interest%20on%20the%20platform%20in%20April.%20Used%20EV%20sales%20rose%2017%25%20year%20over%20year%2C%20while%20used%20hybrid%20sales%20jumped%2029%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESupply%20of%20EVs%20has%20tightened%20sharply%20in%20recent%20months%20as%20demand%20has%20increased.%20CarGurus%20said%20the%20market-day%20supply%20of%20new%20EVs%20has%20fallen%2046%25%20since%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20fuel-efficient%20options%20are%20becoming%20more%20expensive%3A%20used%20EV%20prices%20have%20climbed%20nearly%207%25%20since%20February%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faffordable-vehicles-disappearing-american-car-market-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778583601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a023a0aba7ef34b41f3726b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faffordable-vehicles-disappearing-american-car-market-2026-5%22%