over%20offer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20GameStop%20CEO%20made%20an%20unsolicited%20bid%20for%20the%20e-commerce%20giant%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEBay's%20board%20chairman%20said%20Cohen's%20proposal%20is%20%26quot%3Bneither%20credible%20nor%20attractive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEBay%20has%20turned%20down%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgamestop-ryan-cohen-explains-why-hes-serious-about-ebay-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERyan%20Cohen's%20unsolicited%20offer%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20take%20over%20its%20business%2C%20saying%20it's%20better%20off%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20online%20marketplace%20giant%20said%20in%20a%20Tuesday%20press%20release%20that%20it%20has%20officially%20rejected%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgamestop-ceo-ryan-cohen-net-worth-career-history-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGameStop%20CEO's%3C%2Fa%3E%20%2455.5%20billion%20bid%20for%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20concluded%20that%20your%20proposal%20is%20neither%20credible%20nor%20attractive%2C%26quot%3B%20eBay's%20chairman%2C%20Paul%20Pressler%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20Cohen%2C%20before%20outlining%20six%20factors%20influencing%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20were%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BEBay's%20standalone%20prospects.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20uncertainty%20regarding%20your%20financing%20proposal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20impact%20of%20your%20proposal%20on%20eBay's%20long-term%20growth%20and%20profitability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20leverage%2C%20operational%20risks%2C%20and%20leadership%20structure%20of%20a%20combined%20entity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20resulting%20implications%20of%20these%20factors%20on%20valuation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BGameStop's%20governance%20and%20executive%20incentives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%207%20a.m.%20ET%2C%20GameStop's%20shares%20were%20down%20about%205%25%20in%20premarket%20trading.%20EBay's%20shares%20were%20down%20around%201%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen%20told%20Business%20Insider's%20Sarah%20Needleman%20last%20week%3A%20%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20continue%20doing%20whatever%20I%20need%20to%20do%20in%20order%20to%20buy%20the%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGameStop%20offered%20to%20acquire%20eBay%20for%20%24125%20a%20share%20in%20a%20cash-and-stock%20deal.%20For%20the%20cash%20portion%2C%20it%20pointed%20to%20roughly%20%249.4%20billion%20on%20its%20balance%20sheet%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bhighly-confident%20letter%20from%20TD%20Securities%20for%20up%20to%20%2420%20billion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen%2C%20who%20wants%20to%20serve%20as%20CEO%20of%20the%20combined%20company%2C%20said%20in%20his%20proposal%20that%20he%20could%20deliver%20%242%20billion%20of%20annualized%20cost%20reductions%20within%2012%20months%20of%20the%20deal%20closing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20GameStop's%20roughly%201%2C600%20US%20retail%20locations%20would%20give%20eBay%20a%20%26quot%3Bnational%20network%20for%20authentication%2C%20intake%2C%20fulfillment%2C%20and%20live%20commerce.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChewy's%20billionaire%20cofounder%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgamestop-ryan-cohen-claims-ebay-account-suspended-listings-remain-active-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrolling%20eBay%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20days%2C%20saying%20he's%20raising%20money%20for%20the%20acquisition%20by%20auctioning%20off%20baseball%20cards%20and%20GameStop%20merchandise%20on%20its%20website%2C%20and%20publicly%20complaining%20about%20its%20customer%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20viral%20for%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgamestop-ceo-ryan-cohen-cnbc-interview-bizarre-moments-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eawkward%20CNBC%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20which%20he%20seemed%20reluctant%20to%20explain%20precisely%20how%20the%20deal%20would%20be%20funded%2C%20given%20GameStop's%20market%20value%20is%20around%20%2410%20billion%2C%20and%20eBay%20is%20worth%20nearly%20%2450%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen%20recently%20lost%20one%20of%20his%20biggest%20champions%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-big-short-michael-burry-sold-gamestop-ryan-cohen-ebay-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMichael%20Burry%2C%20the%20investor%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Big%20Short%26quot%3B%20fame%2C%20revealed%20he%20had%20sold%20his%20entire%20GameStop%20stake%20after%20assessing%20Cohen's%20eBay%20proposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurry%2C%20who%20had%20touted%20Cohen's%20potential%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmichael-burry-next-warren-buffett-gamestop-ryan-cohen-acquisition-deal-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20next%20Warren%20Buffett%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20calculated%20that%20the%20deal%20would%20lump%20GameStop%20with%20onerous%20amounts%20of%20leverage%20and%20debt%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20statement%20rejecting%20Cohen's%20bid%2C%20eBay%20chairman%20Pressler%20described%20eBay%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrong%2C%20resilient%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20it%20had%20made%20significant%20progress%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20and%20added%20that%20he%20was%20confident%20that%20its%20existing%20management%20could%20%26quot%3Bcontinue%20to%20drive%20sustainable%20growth%2C%20execute%20with%20discipline%2C%20and%20deliver%20long-term%20value%20for%20our%20shareholders.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGameStop%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Febay-rejects-ryan-cohen-gamestop-55-billion-takeover-offer-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778580934000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F