e%20index%20is%20up%20another%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20more%2C%20the%20increases%20haven't%20been%20solely%20in%20the%20US.%20South%20Korea's%20Kospi%20index%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20outsized%20exposure%20to%20chipmakers%2C%20including%20its%20biggest%20component%2C%20Samsung%20%E2%80%94%20has%20seen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-south-korea-kospi-stock-market-outlook-ai-boom-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etorrid%20gains%20as%20well%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20why%20is%20a%20classic%20case%20of%20supply%20and%20demand.%20AI%20has%20driven%20immense%20demand%20for%20computing%20power%2C%20which%20includes%20a%20range%20of%20semiconductors.%20That's%20resulted%20in%20a%20chip%20shortage%2C%20which%20has%20also%20contributed%20to%20higher%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20chip%20stocks%20were%20having%20a%20moment%20in%20mid-to-late%20April%2C%20they've%20gone%20full-fledged%20supernova%20since.%20Let's%20break%20down%20the%20key%20contributors%2C%20what's%20driven%20them%20so%20much%20higher%2C%20and%20parallels%20to%20the%20dot-com%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2234073780-53a9-43de-8b2a-56f4f3f6a2bf%5C%22%3EThe%20market%20moves%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(All%20figures%20are%20YTD%20through%20Monday)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESandisk%20%2B552%25%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIntel%20%2B251%25%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMicron%20%2B179%25%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESamsung%20%2B137%25%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAMD%20%2B114%25%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKOSPI%20%2B86%25%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESOX%20%2B71%25%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fv0Zgw%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Line%20chart%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fv0Zgw%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22110424c1-367d-4619-8a2c-f09f726239e1%5C%22%3EThe%20turning%20point%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20AI%20mania%20hit%20a%20fever%20pitch%2C%20GPUs%20were%20the%20chips%20that%20commanded%20all%20of%20the%20attention.%20Hence%20Nvidia's%20rapid%20rise%20%E2%80%94%20it%20made%20the%20world's%20most%20popular%20GPUs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20key%20pivot%20around%20the%20chips%20needed%20for%20AI%20came%20near%20the%20start%20of%202026%2C%20when%20a%20new%20model%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-deal-to-use-elon-musks-colossus-data-center%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20off%20agentic%20capabilities.%20Those%20systems%20require%20both%20GPUs%20%E2%80%94%20which%20handle%20massive%20amounts%20of%20mathematical%20computation%20%E2%80%94%20and%20CPUs%2C%20which%20coordinate%20tasks%20and%20manage%20the%20broader%20computing%20environment.%20They%20also%20depend%20heavily%20on%20memory%20chips%20used%20to%20store%20and%20feed%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20to%20now%2C%20and%20shares%20in%20CPU%20and%20memory-chip%20makers%20are%20a%20hot%20commodity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22af7e99b1-1689-4275-8c95-cdf35f226a8f%5C%22%3EThe%20recent%20earnings%20bonanza%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20there's%20no%20substitute%20for%20good%2C%20old-fashioned%20strong%20earnings%20(and%20forward%20guidance).%20The%20chip%20sector%20has%20had%20this%20in%20spades%20recently%2C%20further%20fueling%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaiwan-tsmc-semiconductor-chips-hsinchu-birth-rate-fertility-children-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETSMC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fasml-manager-cuts-layoffs-leaked-doc-chips-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EASML%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fintel-stock-price-record-high-q1-earnigns-ai-cpus-intc-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIntel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Qualcomm%2C%20and%20United%20Microelectronics%20all%20reported%20some%20combination%20of%20impressive%20results%20and%20guidance%20in%20the%20past%20few%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bd7564be-dee0-4b9b-9e89-79f01f8bc38f%5C%22%3EParallels%20to%20the%20dot-com%20era%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20tough%20to%20know%20at%20this%20point%20which%20companies%20and%20stocks%20will%20eventually%20benefit%20the%20most%20from%20AI%20productivity%20gains%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20%26quot%3Bpicks%20and%20shovels%26quot%3B%20trade%20involving%20physical%20assets%20is%20thriving.%20The%20same%20thing%20happened%20around%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-bubble-warning-dot-com-crash-ai-stocks-goldman-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edot-com%20bubble%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20when%20stocks%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcisco-stock-price-crash-25-year-recovery-ai-dotcom-bubble-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECisco%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Sun%20Microsystems%20were%20among%20the%20first%20to%20spike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20key%20differences.%20Companies%20now%20generate%20more%20revenue%2C%20cash%20flow%2C%20and%20profits.%20That's%20helped%20regulate%20valuation%20measures%20like%20price-earnings%20ratio.%20Not%20to%20mention%20efficiencies%20unlocked%20by%20new%20technology%20are%20coming%20quicker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227d48a953-c5ff-4572-9ea5-d6b26924f3fd%5C%22%3EWhat%20about%20Nvidia%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20discussion%20about%20chipmakers%20is%20complete%20without%20a%20mention%20of%20the%20king%20itself.%20While%20chip%20stocks%20have%20soared%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-amazon-nvidia-chips-ai-tpu-trainium-customers-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20surprisingly%20lagged.%20Since%20the%20start%20of%202026%2C%20it's%20the%20third-weakest%20performer%20in%20the%20SOX%20(although%20all%2030%20components%20are%20still%20up%20for%20the%20period).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%2C%20Nvidia%20is%20already%20up%20so%20much.%20Other%20chipmakers%20are%20just%20catching%20up.%20Second%2C%20and%20perhaps%20most%20crucially%2C%20investors%20are%20realizing%20that%20a%20wider%20range%20of%20chips%20are%20critical%20for%20AI%20development%2C%20freeing%20up%20more%20market%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchip-semiconductor-stock-gains-spread-beyond-nvidia-cpu-memory-sandisk-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778579401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0245d7c9dd4cb81cda957f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchip-semiconductor-stock-gains-spread-beyond-nvidia-cpu-memory-sandisk-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sandisk%20is%20up%20552%25%20year-to-date%2C%20while%20Intel%20and%20Micron%20have%20spiked%20more%20than%20175%25.%20Here's%20what%20behind%20the%20move.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jciolli%40businessinsider.com%20(Joe%20Ciolli)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20a%20%2431%20billion%20CIO%20thinks%20Fed%20rate%20cuts%20are%20still%20on%20the%20table%20this%20year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20television%20station%20broadcasts%20Jerome%20Powell%20while%20traders%20work%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0232cfe1443b8dc48e3fbe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENYSE%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EInvestors%20see%20the%20potential%20for%20a%20Fed%20rate%20hike%20due%20to%20the%20inflationary%20impacts%20of%20the%20Iran%20war.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECIO%20Brad%20Long%20argues%20that's%20not%20in%20the%20cards%2C%20though.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20central%20bank%20is%20still%20more%20likely%20to%20cut%20rates%20than%20to%20hike%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20have%20grown%20more%20convinced%20that%20the%20Iran%20war-fueled%20oil%20surge%20has%20dashed%20hopes%20for%20a%20rate%20cut%20this%20year%2C%20but%20a%20chief%20investment%20officer%20thinks%20they%20might%20be%20too%20worried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20recent%20surge%20in%20oil%20prices%2C%20investors%20even%20think%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rate-hike-interest-rates-inflation-outlook-economy-iran-war-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFederal%20Reserve%20could%20hike%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%20According%20to%20the%20CME%20Fedwatch%20Tool%2C%20markets%20are%20pricing%20in%20a%2019%25%20chance%20of%20a%20rate%20hike%20by%20the%20end%20of%202026%2C%20versus%20a%206%25%20chance%20of%20a%20cut.%20By%20April%20next%20year%2C%20odds%20of%20a%20rate%20hike%20spike%20to%2033%25%20compared%20to%20a%204%25%20chance%20of%20the%20Fed%20lowering%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thinking%20is%20that%20high%20oil%20prices%20due%20to%20the%20Iran%20war%20will%20ripple%20through%20the%20economy%20and%20cause%20a%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-economy-consumer-spending-iran-war-us-price-oil-budget-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eflare-up%20of%20inflation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20higher%20oil%20prices%20may%20indeed%20spark%20inflation%2C%20Brad%20Long%2C%20the%20CIO%20at%20Wealthspire%2C%20doesn't%20think%20the%20Fed%20will%20respond%20by%20hiking%20its%20policy%20rate.%20That's%20because%20such%20a%20scenario%20would%20not%20be%20a%20case%20of%20a%20demand-driven%20surge%20in%20consumer%20prices%2C%20he%20said%2C%20meaning%20hiking%20rates%20would%20do%20little%20to%20fix%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20think%20that%20the%20market%20has%20kind%20of%20gotten%20the%20Fed%20side%20of%20the%20equation%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20Long%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Monday%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20believes%20the%20Fed%20is%20aware%20that%20higher%20interest%20rates%20won't%20address%20the%20cause%20of%20higher%20oil%20prices.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20reason%20the%20Fed%20will%20be%20able%20to%20look%20beyond%20any%20rise%20in%20CPI%20data%2C%20Long%20said%2C%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20core%20CPI%20%E2%80%94%20which%20looks%20at%20inflation%20for%20goods%20and%20services%20excluding%20food%20and%20energy%20prices%20%E2%80%94%20is%20still%20subdued%20and%20on%20a%20downtrend.%20In%20March%2C%20it%20hit%202.6%25%2C%20compared%20to%203.3%25%20for%20CPI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20particular%2C%20the%20rise%20in%20shelter%20inflation%E2%80%94the%20largest%20component%20of%20CPI%E2%80%94is%20slowing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%2C%20we%20think%2C%20will%20really%20help%20the%20Fed%20to%20kind%20of%20stay%20where%20they%20are%2C%20or%20maybe%20even%20look%20to%20continue%20to%20cut%20rates%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELong%20said%20that%20higher%20inflation%20expectations%20have%20created%20potential%20opportunities%20in%20short-%20and%20medium-term%20bonds.%20Once%20investors%20recalculate%20a%20lower-rate%20outlook%20from%20the%20Fed%2C%20yields%20on%20shorter-%20and%20medium-duration%20bonds%20should%20fall%2C%20sending%20their%20prices%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20investors%20can%20gain%20exposure%20to%20these%20trades%20is%20through%20exchange-traded%20funds%20like%20the%20Vanguard%20Short-Term%20Bond%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fvanguard-short-term-bond-index-fund-etf-shares-us9219378273%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBSV%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20the%20iShares%20Intermediate%20Govt%2FCredit%20Bond%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fishares-intermediate-government-credit-bond-etf-us4642886125%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGVI%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rate-cuts-outlook-inflation-oil-prices-iran-war-cpi-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778578801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0232d8c9dd4cb81cda94ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rate-cuts-outlook-inflation-oil-prices-iran-war-cpi-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20recognize%2C%20as%20does%20the%20Fed%2C%20that%20the%20cure%20for%20lower%20oil%20is%20not%20higher%20fed%20funds%20rates%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Brad%20Long%2C%20the%20CIO%20at%20Wealthspire.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Quote%20of%20the%20day%20by%20Alfred%20Nobel%3A%20%E2%80%9CA%20heart%20can%20no%20more%20be%20forced%20to%20love%20than%20a%20stomach%20can%20be%20forced%20to%20digest%20food%20by%20persuasion.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778578628000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131035013%2Cimgsize-37530.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fscience%2Fquote-of-the-day-by-alfred-nobel-a-heart-can-no-more-be-forced-to-love-than-a-stomach-can-be-forced-to-digest-food-by-persuasion-%2Farticleshow%2F131034862.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F131034862.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Science%20Desk%