o%2F131034649.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fyou-have-lost-trust-of-public-uk-minister-miatta-fahnbulleh-quits-as-pm-keir-starmer-faces-growing-calls-to-resign%2Farticleshow%2F131034649.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fyou-have-lost-trust-of-public-uk-minister-miatta-fahnbulleh-quits-as-pm-keir-starmer-faces-growing-calls-to-resign%2Famp_articleshow%2F131034649.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fyou-have-lost-trust-of-public-uk-minister-miatta-fahnbulleh-quits-as-pm-keir-starmer-faces-growing-calls-to-resign%2Famp_articleshow%2F131034649.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tariff%20refunds%20are%20about%20to%20start%20rolling%20out.%20Customers%20want%20their%20cut.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224419%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cranes%20for%20handling%20shipping%20containers%20stand%20in%20the%20far%20distance%20as%20the%20Statue%20of%20Liberty%20stands%20in%20the%20middle%20distance%20as%20the%20sun%20sets%20near%20New%20York%20City.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a01f343ba7ef34b41f36fd8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222947%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECompanies%20from%20Costco%20to%20FedEx%20have%20faced%20lawsuits%20from%20customers%20seeking%20their%20share%20of%20the%20refunds.%3Cp%3ECHARLY%20TRIBALLEAU%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20federal%20government%20is%20set%20to%20start%20distributing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftim-cook-apple-tariff-refund-strategy-donald-trump-whisperer-2026-4%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etariff%20refunds%3C%2Fa%3E%20soon.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20companies%20are%20facing%20customer%20lawsuits%20demanding%20their%20share.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20lawsuits%20target%20companies%20from%20Costco%20to%20FedEx.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20are%20set%20to%20start%20getting%20refunds%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-oval-office-white-house-decor-changes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E's%20unconstitutional%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etariffs.%20Some%20customers%20are%20suing%20to%20get%20a%20cut%20of%20the%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%20told%20shippers%20last%20week%20that%20it%20would%20start%20issuing%20refunds%20as%20early%20as%20Tuesday%20to%20companies%20that%20have%20applied.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20agency%20did%20not%20comment%20Monday%20when%20asked%20whether%20it%20was%20on%20track%20to%20issue%20those%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20doesn't%20end%20there%2C%20though.%20Customers%20are%20suing%20some%20companies%20for%20a%20share%C2%A0of%20the%20refunds%20they%20say%20they%20paid%20through%20higher%20prices%20and%20fees%20on%20goods%20and%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENike%20is%20the%20latest%20target.%20Customers%20of%20the%20shoe%20brand%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20company%20on%20Friday%20in%20the%20US%20District%20Court%20for%20the%20District%20of%20Oregon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20names%20seven%20people%20who%20purchased%20Nike%20products%20that%20were%20subject%20to%20the%20tariffs%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20unconstitutional%20in%20February.%20While%20Nike%20said%20last%20year%20that%20it%20expected%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnike-raising-prices-us-expects-1-billion-tariff-hit-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%241%20billion%20hit%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20tariffs%2C%20it%20made%20up%20at%20least%20some%20of%20the%20difference%20by%20raising%20prices%20for%20shoes%20and%20other%20sportswear%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNike%20stands%20to%20recover%20the%20same%20tariff%20payments%20twice%E2%80%94once%20from%20consumers%20through%20higher%20prices%20and%20again%20from%20the%20federal%20government%20through%20tariff%20refunds%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENike%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20or%20respond%20to%20the%20claims%20in%20court%20filings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20companies%20are%20facing%20similar%20lawsuits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-member-sues-for-share-of-tariffs-refund-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECostco%20customer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%20sued%20the%20warehouse%20chain%20in%20March%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20retailer%20is%20similarly%20poised%20to%20recover%20its%20tariff%20costs%20twice%20unless%20it%20refunds%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-ceo-tariff-refunds-members-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECostco%20CEO%20Ron%20Vachris%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20said%20that%20the%20company%20would%20pass%20along%20any%20refunds%20it%20gets%20from%20the%20federal%20government%20in%20the%20form%20of%20%26quot%3Blower%20prices%20and%20better%20values%20for%20members.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffedex-ups-face-lawsuits-customers-tariff-brokerage-fees-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFedEx%20and%20UPS%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20billed%20customers%20for%20tariffs%20on%20US-bound%20shipments%2C%20have%20also%20faced%20suits%20seeking%20refunds%20of%20both%20the%20tariffs%20themselves%20and%20the%20brokerage%20fees%20they%20charged.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20those%20brokerage%20fees%20were%20nearly%20as%20much%20as%20the%20tariffs%20themselves%2C%20according%20to%20one%20of%20the%20lawsuits%20against%20FedEx.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFedEx%20and%20UPS%20have%20said%20they%20will%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-fedex-ups-dhl-plan-to-refund-customers-for-tariffs-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereturn%20tariff%20payments%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20customers%20once%20the%20government%20refunds%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20tariffs%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabitter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eabitter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20via%20encrypted%20messaging%20app%20Signal%20at%20808-854-4501.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehere's%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eguide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftariff-refunds-set-to-land-customers-sue-for-a-cut-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778578381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a01f35eba7ef34b41f36fda%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftariff-refunds-set-to-land-customers-sue-for-a-cut-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Customers%20are%20suing%20Nike%20and%20others%20over%20IEEPA%20tariff%20refunds.%20The%20companies%20are%20facing%20lawsuits%20as%20refund%20payments%20begin%20to%20roll%20out.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abitter%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Bitter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%2