in%202026%20has%20found%20itself%20at%20the%20center%20of%20the%20stock%20market's%20hottest%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20has%20spurred%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmemory-stocks-rally-chips-tech-stock-market-investing-sndk-mu-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ememory%20super%20cycle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20fueling%20massive%20demand%20for%20memory%20and%20data%20storage%20solutions.%20This%20has%20turned%20into%20huge%20gains%20for%20memory%20chipmakers%20like%20Sandisk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memory%20chip%20stock's%20monumental%20rise%20has%20earned%20it%20the%20top%20spot%20as%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20top%20gainer%20year-to-date%2C%20outpacing%20AI%20chip%20darling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fwdc-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia's%3C%2Fa%3E%20gains%20in%20its%202023%20and%202024%20hay%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FlqnXV%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22468%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EShares%20were%20up%20552%25%20year%20to%20date%20at%20the%20closing%20bell%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what's%20going%20on%2C%20and%20why%20are%20investors%20piling%20into%20the%20stock%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220153004a-a594-4e50-9e92-78f8843ab50d%5C%22%3ESandisk's%20place%20in%20the%20AI%20ecosystem%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESandisk%20was%20spun%20out%20of%20Western%20Digital%20in%20February%202025.%20Western%20Digital%20is%20also%20a%20key%20memory%20play%2C%20and%20has%20delivered%20its%20own%20stellar%20stock%20performance%20in%20that%20time.%20It%20pales%20in%20comparison%20to%20Sandisk%2C%20however.%20In%20the%20year%20since%20it%20became%20a%20separate%20public%20company%2C%20Sandisk%20stock%20is%20up%20about%204%2C000%25%2C%20and%20its%20market%20cap%20has%20ballooned%20to%20around%20%24230%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20AI%20boom%20progresses%2C%20needs%20have%20shifted%20from%20training%20to%20inference%2C%20causing%20a%20surge%20in%20demand%20for%20memory%20chips.%20AI%20tech%20relies%20on%20data%20which%20is%20stored%20on%20memory%20chips%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20inference%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESandisk%20occupies%20an%20even%20more%20in-demand%20niche%20within%20the%20memory%20space.%20The%20company%20makes%20NAND%20technology%2C%20memory%20chips%20that%20don't%20require%20power%20to%20store%20data%2C%20including%20SSDs%2C%20which%20are%20storage%20devices%20using%20NAND%20flash%20to%20store%20data%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20traditional%20hard%20drives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20tech%20has%20become%20a%20crucial%20element%20in%20AI%20infrastructure%2C%20driving%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmemory-shortage-chips-cost-laptop-pc-prices-increase-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ememory%20chip%20shortage%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BData%20center%20storage%20has%20shifted%20from%20a%20simple%20two-tier%20model%20-%20HDDs%20for%20capacity%20and%20small%20SSDs%20for%20compute%20-%20to%20a%20three-tier%20architecture%20driven%20by%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Bernstein%20analyst%20Mark%20Newman%20outlined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20AI-driven%20cost%20effective%20third%20tier%20Newman%20is%20talking%20about%20it%20is%20NAND.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20workloads%20created%20strong%20demand%20for%20high-capacity%20enterprise%20SSDs%20to%20support%20data%20prep%20and%20pre-compute%20tasks%20that%20HDDs%20cannot%20handle%2C%20pushing%20new%20AI%20storage%20deployments%20temporarily%20toward%20NAND%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223e3c3f7f-6471-43e1-bdfc-447711933546%5C%22%3ESandisk%20stock%20rides%20inference%20wave%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20its%20latest%20earnings%20call%2C%20Sandisk%20CEO%20David%20Goeckeler%20highlighted%20the%20company's%20position%20in%20the%20NAND%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNAND%20flash%20is%20emerging%20as%20the%20only%20economically%20viable%20solution%20to%20deliver%20that%20capacity%2C%20performance%2C%20and%20efficiency%20required%20to%20keep%20%5BAI%5D%20models%20accessible%20for%20real-time%20inference%20at%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECatalyst%20Funds%20senior%20portfolio%20manager%20David%20Miller%20framed's%20Sandisk's%20AI%20opportunity%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bstorage%20and%20data%20gravity%20trade.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20models%20scale%2C%20data%20storage%20and%20retrieval%20becomes%20the%20next%20choke%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said%2C%20explaining%20that%20Sandisk%20sits%20at%20this%20%26quot%3Binvisible%20layer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20portfolio%20manager%20also%20noted%20that%20any%20shift%20from%20compute%20to%20cloud%2C%20a%20potential%20next%20step%20in%20the%20evolution%20of%20AI%2C%20would%20favor%20NAND%20over%20HDD%20due%20to%20power%20efficiency%20and%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBerstein%20analysts%20expect%20NAND%20prices%20to%20continue%20to%20rise%20on%20the%20supply%20demand%20imbalance%20in%202026%2C%20fueling%20its%20bullish%20outlook%20for%20the%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Sandisk%20has%20seen%20the%20most%20dramatic%20gains%2C%20the%20rally%20has%20lifted%20shares%20of%20other%20companies%20in%20the%20space%2C%20making%20the%20memory%20trade%20this%20year's%20hottest%20stock%20play.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fstx-stock%3F_gl%3D1*17k73on*_ga*MTUzNTgyMTE1Ny4xNzcwOTIyMDY0*_ga_E21CV80ZCZ*czE3Nzg1MTQ5NzAkbzMyMyRnMSR0MTc3ODUxODQ4NiRqNSRsMCRoMA..%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESeagate%20Technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Western%20Digital%20have%20roughly%20tripled%20in%20value%20in%202026%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fmu-stock%5C%22%2