D%5C%22992%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dominique%20Alexander%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a02116ce1443b8dc48e3e60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22744%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDominique%20Alexander%20has%20spent%20years%20searching%20for%20stable%20work%20after%20working%20at%20Microsoft%20and%20Coca-Cola.%3Cp%3EDominique%20Alexander%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDominique%20Alexander%20has%20struggled%20to%20find%20full-time%20work%20after%20roles%20at%20Coca-Cola%20and%20Microsoft.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20years%20of%20job%20searching%20and%20rejection%20hurt%20her%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20taking%20a%20break%20from%20job%20searching%2C%20she%20resumed%20her%20search%20last%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Dominique%20Alexander%2C%20a%20job%20seeker%20in%20her%2040s%20who%20lives%20in%20Louisiana.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20I've%20lost%20multiple%20jobs.%20I'm%20still%20trying%20to%20recover%20from%20the%20financial%20and%20mental%20toll.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20my%20contract%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-careers-jobs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erole%20at%20Microsoft%3C%2Fa%3E%20ended%20in%20late%202021%2C%20I've%20dealt%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20rejection%2C%20which%20can%20really%20mess%20with%20your%20head.%20I've%20read%20that%20for%20humans%2C%20some%20of%20the%20most%20stressful%20types%20of%20situations%20are%20ones%20where%20we%20don't%20know%20how%20long%20they'll%20last.%20This%20is%20part%20of%20why%20job%20searching%20can%20be%20so%20stressful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20piece%20of%20advice%20I%20have%20for%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-market-find-work-employment-hiring-slowdown-careers-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejob%20seekers%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20to%20be%20vulnerable%20about%20what%20you're%20going%20through.%20Telling%20people%20you're%20out%20of%20work%20can%20help%20lead%20to%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e4810af1-2bbb-4509-b8bf-86d2a7a2ab80%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20thought%20having%20a%20connection%20would%20be%20more%20helpful%20in%20landing%20a%20job%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20late%202018%2C%20I%20was%20laid%20off%20from%20my%20finance%20manager%20job%20at%20a%20major%20US%20tobacco%20company.%20As%20I%20looked%20for%20work%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-moving-to-atlanta-from-los-angeles-california-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20Atlanta%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20I%20had%20family%20and%20a%20connection%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoca-cola-ranked-best-place-to-work-career-growth-report-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworked%20at%20Coca-Cola%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20headquartered%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20most%20of%20the%20next%20year%20focused%20on%20getting%20a%20role%20at%20Coca-Cola.%20I%20thought%20my%20inside%20connection%20would%20give%20me%20an%20edge%2C%20but%20despite%20applying%20to%20dozens%20of%20roles%20at%20the%20company%2C%20I%20only%20landed%20a%20couple%20of%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20growing%20concerned%20about%20my%20finances%2C%20but%20that%20summer%2C%20I%20landed%20an%20interview%20for%20a%20senior%20manager%20role%20at%20Coca-Cola.%20After%20months%20of%20interviews%2C%20I%20received%20an%20offer%20%E2%80%94%20and%20started%20in%20November%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20into%20my%20role%2C%20we%20went%20remote%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic%2C%20which%20significantly%20affected%20my%20onboarding%20and%20training.%20I%20navigated%20this%20challenge%20until%20I%20was%20laid%20off%20in%20January%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20is%20speaking%20with%20workers%20who've%20found%20themselves%20at%20a%20corporate%20crossroads%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20due%20to%20a%20layoff%2C%20resignation%2C%20job%20search%2C%20or%20shifting%20workplace%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShare%20your%20story%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSechTVqVWQve8iqYssNriCXdtwwdgGRixNNZpmslSKBQqIJ8g%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dheader%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efilling%20out%20this%20form%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20contacting%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajzinkula%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejzinkula%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20via%20Signal%20at%20jzinkula.29.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aae52982-5ef2-4cd4-b94a-908e7256de71%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20struggled%20to%20find%20work%20and%20took%20part-time%20and%20contract%20roles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20my%20layoff%2C%20I%20began%20looking%20for%20work%20but%20struggled%20to%20find%20any.%20A%20few%20months%20later%2C%20I%20started%20a%20part-time%20role%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-warehouse%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ean%20Amazon%20warehouse%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20earn%20some%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20that%20year%2C%20a%20friend%20of%20mine%20said%20he%20knew%20someone%20at%20a%20small%20consulting%20firm%20who%20was%20looking%20for%20contractors%20to%20work%20at%20Microsoft.%20In%20August%202021%2C%20I%20started%20a%20contract%20role%20as%20a%20finance%20program%20manager.%20But%20in%20November%202021%2C%20my%20contract%20ended%2C%20leaving%20me%20without%20a%20job%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20most%20of%202022%20focused%20on%20landing%20a%20role%20at%20Microsoft.%20I%20thought%20my%20contract%20experience%20would%20give%20me%20an%20edge.%20In%20hindsight%2C%20though%2C%20I%20think%20I%20wasted%20a%20year%20of%20my%20life%3B%20the%20company%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-layoffs-widespread-xbox-azure-government-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaying%20people%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20think%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-hiring-layoffs-amazon-apple-microsoft-google-meta-charts-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehiring%20may%20have%20slowed%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20than%20I%20realized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222e171ee5-d39c-4602-afaa-ef5f9b57ed4f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20took%20a%20break%20from%20job%20hunting%20to%20reset%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBy%202023%2C%20my%20job%20search%20was%20taking%20a%20toll%20on%20my%20finances%20and%20mental%20health%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20scale%20back.%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-new-orleans-built-great-life-after-divorce-love-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20Louisiana%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20into%20a%20home%20my%20parents%20owned.%20This%20helped%20financially%2C%20as%20I%20only%20had%20to%20cover%20maintenance%20and%20utilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20still%20struggling%20mentally%20in%202024%2C%20so%20my%20parents%20and%20I%20agreed%20that%20I%20should%20stay%20off%20LinkedIn%20for%20the%20entire%20year%20and%20not%20think%20about%20job%20hunting.%20I%20tried%20to%20mentally%20decompress%3B%20I%20traveled%20and%20had%20fun%2C%20hoping%20that%20I'd%20be%20in%20a%20good%20headspace%20to%20job%20search%20again%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20beginning%20of%202025%2C%20I've%20hit%20the%20job%20search%20hard%2C%20focusing%20on%20finance%20and%20project%20management%20roles.%20I%20also%20earned%20a%20project%20management%20professional%20certification%2C%20which%20I%20hoped%20would%20help.%20However%2C%20I'm%20still%20looking%20for%20steady%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20I%20started%20a%20seasonal%20tax%20ad