ssa%20Petro%20shares%20her%20perspective%20on%20Botox%2C%20aging%2C%20and%20societal%20beauty%20standards%20for%20women.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20started%20getting%20Botox%20in%202021%20after%20noticing%20that%20her%20face%20would%20distract%20her%20during%20work%20calls.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPetro%20finds%20Botox%20boosts%20her%20confidence%2C%20helping%20her%20focus%20more%20on%20work%20and%20social%20interactions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20get%20older%2C%20I'm%20surprised%20by%20how%20viscerally%20I%20react%20to%20my%20own%20reflection.%20My%20face%20distracts%20me%20on%20Zoom%20calls.%20I%20angle%20the%20camera%20just%20so%20to%20sharpen%20my%20jawline%20and%20soften%20the%20%26quot%3Bmarionette%26quot%3B%20effect.%20I%20understand%20that%20aging%20is%20not%20a%20personal%20failing%2C%20and%20yet%2C%20a%20familiar%20feeling%20arises%20anyway%3A%20shame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20feeling%20I%20know%20well.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penguinrandomhouse.com%2Fbooks%2F736321%2Fshame-on-you-by-melissa-petro%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20wrote%20a%20book%20about%20how%20shame%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20around%20women's%20bodies%20and%20behavior%20%E2%80%94%20is%20internalized%2C%20and%20as%20a%20coach%2C%20I%20see%20how%20even%20those%20of%20us%20who%20recognize%20the%20absurdity%20of%20these%20standards%20are%20still%20affected%20by%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWomen%20my%20age%20(I'm%2046)%20who%20visibly%20try%20%E2%80%94%20who%20dye%20their%20hair%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-go-to-med-spas-abroad-save-money-treatments-injectables-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eget%20injectables%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20wear%20makeup%2C%20or%20invest%20time%20and%20money%20into%20their%20appearance%20%E2%80%94%20are%20often%20dismissed%20as%20vain%2C%20high-maintenance%2C%20or%20insecure.%20Meanwhile%2C%20those%20who%20don't%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20having%20%26quot%3Blet%20themselves%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20women%20who%20exercise%20to%20stay%20fit%2C%20filter%20their%20photos%2C%20or%20follow%20elaborate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-best-skincare-routine-order-according-to-dermatologists-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eskincare%20routines%3C%2Fa%3E%20tend%20to%20draw%20a%20line%20just%20below%20their%20own%20behavior%20and%20judge%20anyone%20who%20crosses%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bd97655f-addc-4f7f-853c-55d15be24f79%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBotox%20has%20started%20to%20feel%20as%20normal%20an%20investment%20as%20a%20regular%20gel%20manicure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBotox%20is%20often%20lumped%20in%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplastic-surgery-c-suite-executives-beauty-trends-look-younger-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplastic%20surgery%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20by%20people%20who%20are%20skeptical%20of%20cosmetic%20procedures%20or%20unfamiliar%20with%20the%20distinctions.%20If%20you%2C%20like%20me%2C%20came%20of%20age%20in%20the%201980s%20%E2%80%94%20before%20medspas%20were%20commonplace%20%E2%80%94%20you%20may%20still%20think%20of%20these%20treatments%20as%20something%20only%20wealthy%20women%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20by%20no%20means%20wealthy%2C%20but%20when%20the%20four-step%20skincare%20routine%20I'd%20adopted%20in%20my%20late%2030s%20stopped%20delivering%2C%20I%20looked%20into%20injectables.%20They%20weren't%20as%20expensive%20as%20I'd%20feared%2C%20or%20as%20dangerous%20as%20some%20people%20made%20them%20sound.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%20nervous%2C%20I%20went%20to%20my%20dermatologist%20for%20the%20first%20time%20instead%20of%20a%20med%20spa%20and%20ended%20up%20paying%20far%20more%20than%20I%20needed%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22747235e4-e872-4fdf-bd89-08b1f0ed3892%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERiding%20home%20on%20the%20subway%2C%20I%20felt%20self-conscious%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20the%20telltale%20%26quot%3Bbee%20sting%26quot%3B%20dots%20across%20my%20forehead.%20Within%20hours%2C%20they%20faded%2C%20and%20within%20days%2C%20my%20skin%20had%20smoothed%20%E2%80%94%20my%20face%20looking%20like%20a%20more%20rested%2C%20slightly%20younger%20version%20of%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202021%2C%20I've%20gone%20every%20six%20to%20eight%20months%20or%20so%20%E2%80%94%20slightly%20less%20often%20than%20recommended%2C%20but%20as%20often%20as%20I%20can%20afford.%20I%20treat%20my%20forehead%2C%20crow's%20feet%2C%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Belevens%26quot%3B%E2%80%94%20those%20vertical%20lines%20between%20the%20eyebrows%20that%20deepen%20when%20you%20frown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20in%2C%20I%20spend%20around%20%24800-%241%2C000%20a%20year.%20It's%20worth%20every%20penny.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221f1da150-6766-4dfb-afec-40354d99cc43%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20never%20had%20a%20bad%20experience%2C%20and%20I%20always%20love%20the%20results%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20recently%2C%20I%20went%20to%20VIO%20Medspa%20in%20Dobbs%20Ferry%2C%20New%20York%2C%20a%20local%20outpost%20of%20a%20larger%20medspa%20chain.%20Walking%20in%2C%20I%20was%20oddly%20reassured%20it%20was%20staffed%20by%20%26quot%3Bnormal%26quot%3B-looking%20women.%20%3Cem%3ENot%20that%20there's%20anything%20wrong%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bplastic%20surgery%20look%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20I%20reminded%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it%20helped%20to%20imagine%20no%20one%20was%20judging%20me%20for%20what%20I%20wasn't%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Egetting%20done%20%E2%80%94%20the%20uneven%20texture%2C%20sagging%20skin%2C%20and%20other%20imperfections%20Botox%20couldn't%20fix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20waited%2C%20I%20spoke%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-flags-bad-facial-signs-from-estheticians-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elicensed%20aesthetician%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20different%20procedures.%20She%20talked%20about%20how%20she%20came%20to%20open%20the%20medspa%20as%20her%20kids%20got%20older%2C%20a%20second%20act%20built%20around%20helping%20women%20feel%20more%20comfortable%20in%20their%20skin.%20We%20talked%20candidly%20about%20Westchester%20real%20estate%2C%20taking%20kids%20on%20college%20visits%2C%20and%20the%20slow%20practice%20of%20letting%20go%20of%20control.%20The%20space%20felt%20easy%20and%20unguarded%2C%20like%20the%20female%20equivalent%20of%20going%20to%20the%20barbershop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20procedure%20itself%20took%20a%20minute%20or%20two.%20I%20didn't%20feel%20any%20pain%2C%20just%20a%20series%20of%20small%20pinches.%20The%20results%20appeared%20about%20two%20weeks%20later.%20I%20plan%20to%20go%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f289a3bb-0886-45ee-8b27-655a168ff1c6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20I%20need%20it%3F%20No%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20anyone%20needs%20anything%20done.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20think%20it's%20everyone's%20right%20to%20do%20what%20they%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I've%20had%20Botox%2C%20I%20spend%20less%20time%20scrutinizing%20myself%20on%20camera.%20I%20can%20jump%20into%20a%20meeting%20without%20adjusting%20the%20angle%2C%20the%20lighting%2C%20or%20my%20posture.%20I'm%20more%20present%20with%20my%20clients%20because%20I'm%20less%20preoccupied%20with%20how%20I%20look.%20I've%20thought%20about%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacelift-34-why-i-did-it-south-korea-surgery-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efacelift%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20Botox%20is%20doing%20the%20job%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20in%20my%20social%20circle%20gets%20Botox%2C%20and%20my%20husband%20says%20he%20doesn't%20see%20a%20difference.%20I%20don't%20expect%20that%20my%20clients%20can%20put%20a%20finger%20on%20it%20either%2C%20but%20I'm%20confident%20they%20appreciate%20it%20when%20I%20show%20up%20with%20a%20more%20polished%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2234786624-39a6-4295-ab03-9d13b2ce5e41%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20can%20pretend%20appearance%20doesn't%20matter%2C%20but%20it%20does%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAppearance-based%20shame%20remains%20powerful%2C%20even%20among%20people%20who%20reject%20beauty%20standards.%20Across%20the%20political%20spectrum%2C%20people%20mock%20and%20police%20others'%20looks%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20those%20they%20dislike%20or%20see%20as%20powerful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20passes%20as%20critique%20is%20often%20a%20form%20of%20self-protection%3A%20shaming%20someone%20else's%20appearance%20can%20momentarily%20soothe%20our%20own%20anxiety%20about%20aging%2C%20visibility%2C%20and%20physical%20change%2C%20even%20as%20it%20deepens%20the%20harmful%20link%20between%20beauty%20and%20virtue.%20Over%20time%2C%20this%20culture%20of%20shame%20takes%20a%20real%20toll%20on%20mental%20health%2C%20especially%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20long%20for%20a%20world%20where%20we%20resist%20harshly%20judging%20people%20for%20how%20they%20look%2C%20where%20we%20can%20disagree%20without%20turning%20someone's%20face%20into%20evidence%2C%20and%20where%20aging%20isn't%20treated%20as%20a%20moral%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20I%20put%20my%20best%20face%20forward%20in%20the%20world%20as%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fget-botox-feel-more-confident-work-wrinkles-distract-me-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778576702000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb9c2f3cfefc31768d6518%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fget-botox-feel-more-confident-work-wrinkles-distract-me-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Melissa%20Petro%20noticed%20her%20skincare%20routine%20wasn't%20cutting%20it%20in%20her%20late%2030s.%20She%20looked%20into%20injectables%20and%20now%20gets%20Botox%20as%20often%20as%20she%20can.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Melissa%20Petro)%22%2C%2