by%20the%20dangerously%20high%20levels%20of%20the%20Sutlej%2C%20Beas%2C%20and%20Ravi%20rivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20is%20drowning.%20It%20needs%20your%20help.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FDisaster-Relief%2FThe-Better-India%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Clabel%3EDONATE%20NOW%20%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDonate%20to%20help%20Punjab%20flood%20victims%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmer%20Mohan%2C%20like%20the%203%2C54%2C000%20people%20(as%20of%205%20September)%20affected%2C%20did%20not%20have%20time%20to%20grieve.%20His%20only%20priority%20was%20ensuring%20that%20his%20family%20made%20it%20out%20of%20the%20house%20alive.%20But%20there%20was%20no%20escape%3B%20the%20only%20option%20was%20to%20wait%20and%20pray.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A496899%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20they%20saw%20a%20boat%20making%20its%20way%20to%20them.%20In%20it%20was%20Simranjit%20Singh%2C%20part%20of%20the%20Akal%20Relief%20Team%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F391684%2Fcol-dr-rajinder-singh-started-akal-drug-de-addiction-centre-punjab-substance-abuse-alcoholism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPunjab-based%20NGO%20Kalgidhar%20Trust%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20many%20conducting%20relief%20and%20rescue%20operations%20on%20the%20ground%20supported%20by%20Donatekart.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20possibility%20of%20salvaging%20the%20house%20or%20any%20of%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20belongings.%20But%20as%20they%20journeyed%20on%20the%20boat%20to%20the%20relief%20camp%20in%20Gurdaspur%2C%20Mohan%20broke%20down%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20fields%20are%20gone.%20I%20know%20I%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20sow%20anything%20for%20another%20year%20until%20the%20soil%20becomes%20fertile%20again%20and%20the%20mud%20is%20removed.%20What%20am%20I%20going%20to%20do%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-1-1757073005.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Relief%20and%20rescue%20operations%20are%20ongoing%20on%20ground%20to%20help%20the%20people%20affected%20by%20the%20Punjab%20floods%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-1-1757073005.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-1-1757073005-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-1-1757073005-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-1-1757073005-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-1-1757073005-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496937%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERelief%20and%20rescue%20operations%20are%20underway%20to%20support%20people%20affected%20by%20the%20Punjab%20floods.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20had%20the%20answers.%20Harmeet%20Singh%2C%20who%20leads%20CSR%20(Corporate%20Social%20Responsibility)%20at%20Kalgidhar%20Trust%2C%20admits%20that%2C%20despite%20having%20conducted%20relief%20and%20rescue%20operations%20for%20the%20last%20two%20decades%2C%20they%20are%20daunted%20by%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20calamity%20%E2%80%94%20these%20are%20being%20called%20the%20worst%20floods%20that%20the%20city%20has%20experienced%20since%201988.%20As%20of%202%3A30%20PM%20on%205%20September%202025%2C%20the%20death%20toll%20stands%20at%2043%2C%20with%201%2C48%2C000%20hectares%20of%20agricultural%20land%20submerged%20under%20water%20and%20with%20it%2C%20thousands%20of%20dreams.%20Punjab%20is%20the%20seat%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20agrarian%20economy%2C%20and%20a%20calamity%20of%20this%20scale%20will%20ripple%20into%20effects%20that%20are%20felt%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20will%20take%20time%20to%20bring%20the%20situation%20under%20control%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20joining%20hands%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EDonatekart%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20to%20help.%20And%20you%20can%20join%20us%20too%2C%20by%20donating%20to%20this%20fundraiser.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FDisaster-Relief%2FThe-Better-India%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Clabel%3EDONATE%20NOW%20%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelp%20the%20people%20of%20Punjab%3A%20What%20can%20you%20do%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FDisaster-Relief%2FThe-Better-India%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20this%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20donate%20to%20the%20fundraiser.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%